Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Que bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja hi som!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ooooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ooooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.84,White,,0,0,0,,Que brillant!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Ostres!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.52,White,,0,0,0,,-És en Nobunaga Oda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:25.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'any 2017 se celebra\Nel 450è aniversari
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"de la triomfal entrada\Ndel general Nobunaga Oda,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,del període Sengoku,\Nal castell de Gifu."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"A més de visitar la ciutat,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:34.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"aprofitem per assistir a alguns\Ndels esdeveniments commemoratius
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que hi tenen lloc."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:02.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ha sigut molt interessant,\Noi que sí, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, i tant que sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:08.72,White,,0,0,0,,Vaja, no sabia que t'agradessin\Naquesta mena de coses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.88,White,,0,0,0,,Últimament hi ha moltes noies\Nque s'interessen per la història.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.68,White,,0,0,0,,Per la història en general\Ni també pel període Sengoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.76,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs, la veritat,\Naixò no us ho sabria dir,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.08,White,,0,0,0,,però jo ho he trobat\Nmolt interessant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Síííí!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Vinga, continuem la visita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.36,White,,0,0,0,,(riuen)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:30.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"S'aixeca el teló\Ni apareix el protagonista."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:32.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Resol els misteris\Nfent una dansa preciosa."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un cas projecta una ombra\Nsobre els nous herois de Gifu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,els Nobuna Gaizers."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:42.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:49.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Amai uso nara tsuiteite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:57.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu wa setsunaku itai mono DA-KA-RA Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aimai, my, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Isso kimi no subete wo kakete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:09.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,logical na watashi\Nwo damashi nuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kitto hajime wa mujaki na koi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,eforume shite mita dake soushite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hikari wo matoi yami ni obieru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,ginmaku sutaa no you ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:38.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sou yo kono mama kyokou no sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:45.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,nazo wo tokeba oikakeru\Nriyuu ga nakunaru wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:54.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nani mo kamo omoidoori\Nnante tsumaranai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why? Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:03.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuwari demo kamawanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:11.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El cas Nobunaga, 450è aniversari"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.24,White,,0,0,0,,Aquí és on dormirem aquesta nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.44,White,,0,0,0,,Benvinguts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.88,White,,0,0,0,,Hola, moltes gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.68,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Tobayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:29.04,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hola, Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:33.20,White,,0,0,0,,Nois, el senyor Tobayama és\Namic meu de fa molts anys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.48,White,,0,0,0,,És ell qui ens ha convidat a venir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.76,White,,0,0,0,,És mestre pescador amb corb marí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.24,White,,0,0,0,,Hola, nois. Sou la Lliga\Nde Detectius Júnior, oi que sí?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.32,White,,0,0,0,,Molt de gust de coneixe'l!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.04,White,,0,0,0,,Vaja! Quina colla més animada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.96,White,,0,0,0,,Hehehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Que bonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Fantàstic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.96,White,,0,0,0,,Mireu, és en Tobayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.20,White,,0,0,0,,Senyor Tobayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.68,White,,0,0,0,,A veure...\Ni ara on "ikomaika"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.88,White,,0,0,0,,Això és el dialecte de Gifu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ikomaika" no es pot\Nfer servir en forma de pregunta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:28.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,En realitat vol dir\N"anem a un lloc".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.80,White,,0,0,0,,Com sempre, tu ho saps tot,\Noi, senyor detectiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Més o menys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:36.32,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, nois,\Njo ja estic mort de gana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.48,White,,0,0,0,,Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.32,White,,0,0,0,,Genta, però si fa poc t'has menjat\N3 plats de carn de bou de Hida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ah, sí? Hehehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.28,White,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:51.16,White,,0,0,0,,Per cert, hi ha un lloc on m'agradaria moltíssim anar, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.52,White,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.68,White,,0,0,0,,Nobunaga va entrar triomfalment\Nal castell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.40,White,,0,0,0,,ara fa quatre-cents...\Ncinquanta anys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.12,White,,0,0,0,,I aquest any es commemora\Naquesta gesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.28,White,,0,0,0,,Que la justícia\Ni l'amistat regnin en aquesta terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.92,White,,0,0,0,,Us portem valor i esforç!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.08,White,,0,0,0,,I també, amor i alegria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.28,White,,0,0,0,,Som l'esquadró origami.\NEls Nobuna Gaizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.72,White,,0,0,0,,Visca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Visca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Visca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Fantàstics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Que bé! Els Nobuna Gaizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Molt bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah! Un espectacle de superherois.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.56,White,,0,0,0,,Els... Nobu... Noza? Com es diuen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.64,White,,0,0,0,,Nobuna Gaizers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:40.16,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que s'han inspirat una mica\Nen en Nobunaga Oda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.76,White,,0,0,0,,Són increïbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.72,White,,0,0,0,,Tu també ho penses?\NDe fet jo volia venir per això.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Fantàstic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Bufa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.72,White,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, l'has fet tot tu sol,\Naquest àlbum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.68,White,,0,0,0,,M'agrada recollir informació\Ndels herois locals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.28,White,,0,0,0,,ho faig sempre que viatjo\Na alguna altra prefectura
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.44,White,,0,0,0,,i també els busco per internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.36,White,,0,0,0,,És una col·lecció enorme.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.00,White,,0,0,0,,Amb tants herois, la Terra ha de ser un lloc supersegur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.76,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.60,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Són increïbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.28,White,,0,0,0,,-(Ayumi) Quina passada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.28,White,,0,0,0,,-(Genta) Ostres, és increïble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.20,White,,0,0,0,,Viiiisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.56,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.12,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.00,White,,0,0,0,,Nobuna Gaizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:34.00,White,,0,0,0,,(crits d'entusiasme)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:40.44,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest és el seu moviment més famós,\Nla triple torre Gaizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Genials!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Són increïbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.60,White,,0,0,0,,-(Ayumi) Jo també.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.60,White,,0,0,0,,-(Mitsuhiko) Deixeu que us ajudi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.68,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Jo també vull ajudar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.04,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.04,White,,0,0,0,,Els Nobuna Gaizers tenim\Nun regal per vosaltres.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:07:00.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Poseu-vos en fila.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:07:00.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Sisplau, agafeu-lo abans de marxar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.92,White,,0,0,0,,-(nen) Gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.92,White,,0,0,0,,-(dona) Teniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.96,White,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh, quin paper més bonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Té, per tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.48,White,,0,0,0,,És paper japonès de Mino, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.88,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Em sorprèn que el coneguis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.24,White,,0,0,0,,És que... abans de venir a veure\Nla vostra actuació,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.32,White,,0,0,0,,he mirat els llocs on havíeu actuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Caram!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.24,White,,0,0,0,,M'alegro de sentir-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:31.04,White,,0,0,0,,Si no fos per gent com tu,\Nno podríem existir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.36,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.80,White,,0,0,0,,Eeh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:38.04,White,,0,0,0,,No, moltes gràcies a vosaltres!\NEstic emocionat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.68,White,,0,0,0,,Moltíssimes gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.32,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies a tots! A reveure, nois!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Adeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Adeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Caram, no havia vist mai\Nen Mitsuhiko tan emocionat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Molt bé, nois!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja estem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí que ha anat bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Ha anat molt bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja hem acabat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Molt bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.04,White,,0,0,0,,Sí! Us felicito, nois!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:07.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.92,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.56,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ens hem de reunir\Nper preparar l'actuació de demà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.92,White,,0,0,0,,Així que pugueu,\Nveniu al meu despatx.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.52,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Entesos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:37.32,White,,0,0,0,,Va contra les normes espiar\Nles cares dels herois, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.84,White,,0,0,0,,Au, vinga, nois, tornem a l'hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.48,White,,0,0,0,,Sííí!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.32,White,,0,0,0,,Que plena que estic, he menjat molt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, jo també.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.88,White,,0,0,0,,Sí?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.40,White,,0,0,0,,Mireu, doncs jo podria\Ncontinuar menjant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:57.04,White,,0,0,0,,Doctor, abans d'arribar a l'hotel\Npodríem parar a comprar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.00,White,,0,0,0,,Em vindria de gust...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.56,White,,0,0,0,,un panet de carn,\Nuns quants entrepans,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.64,White,,0,0,0,,patates fregides i un suc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.56,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord, entesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.84,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Genta,\Nem sembla que menges massa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.68,White,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.80,White,,0,0,0,,Què et passa, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:17.92,White,,0,0,0,,Els hi volia demanar que em firmessin l'àlbum i me n'he descuidat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.76,White,,0,0,0,,No m'ho puc creure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:24.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però, escolta, Mitsuhiko, de debò\Nque et penses rendir tan fàcilment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí. I tant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Au va, que t'esperem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.44,White,,0,0,0,,Però després hem d'anar\Na comprar menjar, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:33.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(Agasa) Ves amb compte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:33.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.96,White,,0,0,0,,Disculpin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.60,White,,0,0,0,,Els membres dels Nobuna Gaizers\Nsón... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.36,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.60,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) En Mitsuhiko\Nestà trigant molt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.68,White,,0,0,0,,Estic a punt de morir-me de gana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.24,White,,0,0,0,,Quin silenci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.20,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Provem de trucar-li.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:15.40,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:15.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Mira! És d'en Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què deu haver passat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.00,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.24,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.24,White,,0,0,0,,Encara no l'heu trobat?\NJa han passat dues hores.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.36,White,,0,0,0,,He avisat\Nels meus companys pescadors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.56,White,,0,0,0,,Si veuen o senten alguna cosa\Nens avisaran immediatament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Han avisat la policia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Moltíssimes gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:44.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'Agasa ha aprofitat les influències d'en Kogoro perquè el busquin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No crec que triguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.72,White,,0,0,0,,(cotxe: sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.40,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.68,White,,0,0,0,,Caram. Em soneu... d'alguna cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, esclar. Jo també.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí! Ara me'n recordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,Ens vam conèixer\Nen el cas del poble d'Onizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.88,White,,0,0,0,,És l'inspector Matsushiro, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.60,White,,0,0,0,,Eh... Per cert, no és amb vosaltres,\Nel senyor Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No, no hi és. Però hem vingut\Namb el doctor Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ah, el doctor Agasa.\NHe sentit a parlar de vostè.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.76,White,,0,0,0,,També ha resolt\Nuns quants casos complicats, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.60,White,,0,0,0,,Diuen que és tan bo fent deduccions\Ncom el senyor Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.52,White,,0,0,0,,Bé, jo no diria tant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Soc jo qui fa la feina\Nen els dos casos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.64,White,,0,0,0,,Et sentiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.60,White,,0,0,0,,Em podeu explicar com ha anat tot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:37.80,White,,0,0,0,,Continuem sense saber\Non és en Mitsuhiko. A més...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Els Nobuna Gaizers també\Nhan desaparegut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.56,White,,0,0,0,,Però què ha passat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.04,White,,0,0,0,,Volíem parlar amb ells\Nper si en sabien alguna cosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.16,White,,0,0,0,,però ens ha estat totalment\Nimpossible contactar-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Tot plegat comença a ser inquietant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.80,White,,0,0,0,,Tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(dos trets)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(alarma)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.68,White,,0,0,0,,(alarma: continua)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.56,White,,0,0,0,,(home) D'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.84,White,,0,0,0,,Els objectes robats...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:19.44,White,,0,0,0,,són una estatueta de Nobunaga\Nd'or massís i la placa d'or,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.60,White,,0,0,0,,a més de documents antics\Nde gran valor històric.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.72,White,,0,0,0,,Tot això forma part\Ndel preuat tresor de Gifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:29.20,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que ens afanyem o aviat\Nho hauran venut tot al mercat negre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.36,White,,0,0,0,,O exportat a l'estranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Això pinta cada cop pitjor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.48,White,,0,0,0,,-De debò?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.92,White,,0,0,0,,Hahaha! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.68,White,,0,0,0,,Daixò...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.80,White,,0,0,0,,Que ens podria ensenyar les imatges de la càmera de seguretat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:46.88,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.40,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres! Però si són...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:54.20,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Els Nobuna Gaizers.\NNo m'ho crec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.48,White,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.12,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,Què? No pot ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.60,White,,0,0,0,,Costa de creure,\Nuns herois que cometen un robatori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.04,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Que dolents!\NNo se sortiran amb la seva!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,(Matsushiro) Què... què dius...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.80,White,,0,0,0,,Que heu trobat\Nel vehicle dels Nobuna Gaizers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.32,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.76,White,,0,0,0,,Què és això?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.04,White,,0,0,0,,-(Ayumi) Pot ser la d'en Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.04,White,,0,0,0,,-(Genta) És la insígnia de Nobunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.44,White,,0,0,0,,Vols dir que ha pujat\Nen aquesta furgoneta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Potser el retenen com a ostatge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, ja me n'he adonat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.24,White,,0,0,0,,Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.96,White,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,A més, mira les rodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.76,White,,0,0,0,,Creus que és...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:56.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,N'estic segur,\Naixò és quitrà d'asfaltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.56,White,,0,0,0,,(home) "Els Nobuna Gaizers,\Nels populars herois locals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.60,White,,0,0,0,,"coneguts per netejar la ciutat\Ni també per ajudar la gent gran,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:07.20,White,,0,0,0,,estan buscats com a sospitosos\Nd'un cas de robatori."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.96,White,,0,0,0,,"Es creu que els seus 5 membres,\Nfugits de la justícia,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.76,White,,0,0,0,,retenen com a ostatge\Nun nen de primària."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És culpa meva, pel que li vaig dir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:21.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però, escolta, Mitsuhiko, de debò\Nque et penses rendir tan fàcilment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí. I tant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Au va, que t'esperem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.20,White,,0,0,0,,Però després hem d'anar\Na comprar menjar, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.20,White,,0,0,0,,-(Agasa) Ves amb compte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.96,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs jo també en soc culpable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Jo tampoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Jo tampoc el vaig aturar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.00,White,,0,0,0,,No, ni jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:42.20,White,,0,0,0,,Uns herois, i què més?!\NSón una colla de pesats. Hehehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per cert, el Nobuna Gaizer vermell era esquerrà, oi que sí?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, però el del robatori era dretà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.72,White,,0,0,0,,A més, quan han fet\Nla seva posició característica...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.88,White,,0,0,0,,el Blau i el Verd estaven al revés.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.56,White,,0,0,0,,Què voleu dir amb això?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.64,White,,0,0,0,,-...siguin impostors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.64,White,,0,0,0,,-¿Pot ser que...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, exactament.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.64,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.28,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:28.20,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta, sou els Nobuna Gaizers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.92,White,,0,0,0,,Xsst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:34.84,White,,0,0,0,,(pip, pip, pip, pip, pip)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.52,White,,0,0,0,,Hola. Està tot preparat.\NNosaltres ens ocuparem de tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:43.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Els impostors van segrestar\Nels autèntics Nobuna Gaizers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,els hi han pres els vestits\Ni han comès el robatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Però, qui ho pot haver fet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Colla de desgraciats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.80,White,,0,0,0,,Tu ja sospites qui és el culpable,\Noi? T'agradaria confirmar-ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí. Doctor,\Ntruqui a l'inspector Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.36,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ja està. Tot ha anat molt bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.92,White,,0,0,0,,Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.16,White,,0,0,0,,-(Ai) Què és el que ha anat bé?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Podria ser el seu pla malvat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.96,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, vostè els hi va parar una trampa\Nals Nobuna Gaizers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:21.20,White,,0,0,0,,i ho ha organitzat tot perquè semblés\Nque havien sigut ells els lladres.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:25.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Però-però... es pot saber qui sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:25.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Tinc raó, senyor Kimifusa Oyabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.48,White,,0,0,0,,-On és en Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.48,White,,0,0,0,,-La Lliga de Detectius Júnior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:32.88,White,,0,0,0,,No... no sé de què parleu.\NJo no sé res.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.76,White,,0,0,0,,És inútil, no dissimuli.\NEn tenim proves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.20,White,,0,0,0,,Proves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.60,White,,0,0,0,,El Nobuna Gaizer vermell\Nés esquerrà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.96,White,,0,0,0,,I quan han fet la figura, el Blau\Ni el Verd estaven intercanviats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.88,White,,0,0,0,,Si volia que es fessin passar\Nper ells,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.72,White,,0,0,0,,els hauria d'haver estudiat millor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.40,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs, potser\Nés que s'han equivocat de posició.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.00,White,,0,0,0,,A més, hi ha una altra prova.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.96,White,,0,0,0,,Una prova que és concloent.\NEl seu anell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.56,White,,0,0,0,,Exacte. Se l'hauria d'haver tret.\NEls herois no porten aquestes coses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.36,White,,0,0,0,,A més a més, ha pegat a un vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.56,White,,0,0,0,,I quan ho ha fet\Nse li ha esquinçat el guant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.28,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que concorda\Namb la ferida de la víctima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.84,White,,0,0,0,,Després de la trucada del doctor\NAgasa ho he tornat a confirmar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.80,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat,\Nel guant del vestit està esquinçat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.00,White,,0,0,0,,Haurem de procedir a analitzar\Nl'anell a fons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.56,White,,0,0,0,,No tenia alternativa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.72,White,,0,0,0,,L'empresa no anava bé,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.84,White,,0,0,0,,els cobradors de l'usurer que em va deixar diners em van amenaçar i...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:36.40,White,,0,0,0,,O sigui, que els altres impostors\Neren de l'empresa de préstecs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.20,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, esclar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.80,White,,0,0,0,,Ho vaig fer\Nperquè em van obligar a ajudar-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.88,White,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa, estic impressionat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:48.76,White,,0,0,0,,Bé, tampoc crec\Nque n'hi hagi per tant. Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Encara no està tot resolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I en Mitsuhiko?\NOn són els autèntics Nobuna Gaizers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.84,White,,0,0,0,,-No... no ho sé, on són.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.84,White,,0,0,0,,-On són?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:01.52,White,,0,0,0,,M'han dit que ells s'ocuparien\Nde la resta. És la veritat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.52,White,,0,0,0,,Què, Conan? Què passa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh? Però què... Ostres!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ens hem d'afanyar o el mataran\Njuntament amb els herois,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:11.12,White,,0,0,0,,segurament\Nno deuen voler deixar cap prova!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Recerca d'emergència!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.00,White,,0,0,0,,(pip, pip)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.60,White,,0,0,0,,Foc! Foc!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.64,White,,0,0,0,,No ens en sortirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:26.40,White,,0,0,0,,-No vull morir! No vull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:26.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Estem perduts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:31.00,White,,0,0,0,,No us heu de rendir! Els fans\Ndels Nobuna Gaizers us esperen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.72,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Conan. Ara què hem de fer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:39.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,N'estic segur,\Naixò és quitrà d'asfaltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Esperi! Pari! Em pot dir on\Nhan estat treballant aquest matí?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja està!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Una mica més, ja falta poc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.56,White,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.04,White,,0,0,0,,(cops)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.08,White,,0,0,0,,-(dona) Auxili!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.08,White,,0,0,0,,-(Mitsuhiko) Ei! Que hi ha algú?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Alguna cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.84,White,,0,0,0,,-I ara què fem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Podem fer servir els papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Allà dalt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aquest matí les zones que han estat\Nasfaltant han sigut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:15.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Són en direccions oposades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:15.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquestes: allà i allà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.64,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) En quina deu ser,\Nen Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:21.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què és allò?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.36,White,,0,0,0,,Aah! Aaai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:30.44,White,,0,0,0,,-No caurem, no pateixis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:30.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Estigues tranquil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Vinga, aguanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Has de confiar en nosaltres!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aguanta, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:45.92,White,,0,0,0,,-I ara què farem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:45.92,White,,0,0,0,,-Ostres, se'ns ha acabat el paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.72,White,,0,0,0,,El meu àlbum!\NAgafeu els fulls del meu àlbum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.40,White,,0,0,0,,Però és un àlbum\Nmolt important per tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.96,White,,0,0,0,,Els herois hi són\Nper ajudar en moments com aquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És aquí!\NHan de ser molt a prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aquest full... és d'en Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.84,White,,0,0,0,,-(nens) Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Venia d'allà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.28,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.36,White,,0,0,0,,Conan, allà! La porta està tancada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Entesos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.64,White,,0,0,0,,Ens heu vingut a salvar.\NEstic molt content.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:24.28,White,,0,0,0,,He passat molta por! Molta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.12,White,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.00,White,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:39.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to nara\Nitsumade mo yume wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:45.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,aruite yukitai to negau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:54.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nee tatoeba juunen mirai no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:21:02.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,bokura wa dou shiteiru ka na.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yume no meiro nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,doa no soto kimi ga ite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,waratteru ka na.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:16.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to nara\Nitsumade mo yume wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:22.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,aruite yukitai to negau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:28.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima mo boku wa yume no naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:35.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oikakete oikakete doko made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:39.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,mada minu keshiki wo mezasu yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:48.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sore ga boku no yume\Nkimi to zutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:51.44,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.76,White,,0,0,0,,Realment ets el nostre heroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.36,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:59.00,White,,0,0,0,,És un gran honor. Moltes gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:01.36,White,,0,0,0,,Han detingut la resta d'impostors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.84,White,,0,0,0,,i s'han recuperat\Ntots els tresors de Gifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:07.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I el bon nom dels herois locals,\Nels Nobuna Gaizers, s'ha restablert.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.64,White,,0,0,0,,Molt bé, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.28,White,,0,0,0,,Ets l'orgull de la Lliga\Nde Detectius Júnior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:16.84,White,,0,0,0,,Per què la Lliga de Detectius Júnior no porteu també un vestit especial?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:18.80,White,,0,0,0,,Apareixen els herois! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Jo també.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.52,White,,0,0,0,,Jo passo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:24.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Doncs mira que jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:24.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Ni pensar-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:26.96,White,,0,0,0,,Som els herois locals,\Nels Nobuna Gaizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:29.20,White,,0,0,0,,Més un!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"...el missatge en clau
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:34.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que va deixar en Koji Haneda\Nfa 17 anys abans de morir."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Una parella estranya?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.88,White,,0,0,0,,Perquè en aquella llibreta,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:41.92,White,,0,0,0,,el foraster hi havia escrit\Nben clara la paraula "nue"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:44.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir\Nque el Nue viu en aquest bosc?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:47.96,White,,0,0,0,,És el monstre enorme i esgarrifós que surt a les llegendes tradicionals?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:51.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:56.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:59.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'En Conan, en Heiji\Ni la llegenda del Nue (El crit)'."
